title: DAZ3D - Poser - Sadie and Sam Ultra Outfit - (DAZ 15056) - DIM (
description:
This Ultra Outfit is many outfits in one. With morphs and material zones to customize the outfit, it can be used to create various length pants and tops.

With the included intelligent randomizer script, hundred of outfit combinations are available at the click of your mouse.

The randomizer script makes clever color choices and even matches up seam colors to the clothing style.
